data.title: Rare Film Posters
data.meta_description: Original British 30 inch x 40 inch Quad Poster for the 1972 Cliff Robertson Western J.W. COOP starring Cliff Robertson, Geraldine Page, Cristina Ferrare, R.G. Armstrong, John Crawford and Wode Crosby. Robertson plays J.W. Coop who sets out to win the rodeo riding national championship after a ten-year spell in jail. The poster is in fine folded condition.
data.text:
Original British 30 inch x 40 inch Quad Poster for the 1972 Cliff Robertson Western J.W. COOP starring Cliff Robertson, Geraldine Page, Cristina Ferrare, R.G. Armstrong, John Crawford and Wode Crosby.

Robertson plays J.W. Coop who sets out to win the rodeo riding national championship after a ten-year spell in jail.

The poster is in fine folded condition.

Original British 30 inch x 40 inch Quad Poster
